																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">12</div> <div class="vers-content">So that the king, and they that were with him, wondered at the young manâ€™s courage, because he esteemed the torments as nothing.</div></div></td>
																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">12</div> <div class="vers-content">Well might they marvel, king and courtiers both, at one so young that recked so little of his sufferings.</div></div></td>
								</tr><tr>									<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">13</div> <div class="vers-content">Et hoc ita defuncto, quartum vexabant similiter torquentes.</div></div></td>
